name: The Voiceless Whisperers
description:
The Voiceless Whisperers are cruel as they are insidious.
Ghostly and ellusive, these creatures slowly worm their way into their victim's mind.
From that point onwards, be it inside or outside the dream, one will be plagued by intrusive and demoralizing thoughts, thoughts one will consider his own.
Should one be broken by this experience, his mind will shatter and he will become little more than a hollow vessel.
And so, the Voiceless Whisperers will have obtained a body and voice of their own.
